{
  "name": "unify-lifecycle-engine",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-27T13:01:02.393Z",
  "description": "Introduce a shared LifecycleEngine in @specd/core to centralize lifecycle interpretation, dependency-aware artifact status, blockers, routing, and next-action decisions across status, context, transitions, validation, and artifact guidance. This removes schema/DAG-aware lifecycle logic from Change, aligns CLI and agent-facing surfaces with one authority, and adds focused debug logging plus coverage around the new engine-backed behavior.",
